few examples of AIs, many of which you’re probably&nbsp;
familiar with. Virtual assistants like Siri,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:02:24.400 --> 00:02:30.320
Alexa, and Google Assistant all use AI. They&nbsp;
help you perform tasks like setting reminders,&nbsp;&nbsp;

