00:02:47.640 --> 00:02:53.240
tastes. Just as you might recommend a show, video,&nbsp;
or product to a friend based on what you know&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:02:53.240 --> 00:02:59.840
about them, these AIs perform a similar role on a&nbsp;
much larger scale. By learning from your viewing,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:02:59.840 --> 00:03:04.400
searching, and purchasing habits, they&nbsp;
continuously refine their recommendations&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:03:04.400 --> 00:03:11.120
to offer suggestions they think you’ll enjoy.&nbsp;
Self-driving cars and robotics, such as Tesla's&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:03:11.120 --> 00:03:17.240
full self-driving and Waymo, rely on AI to&nbsp;
process sensor data, make real-time decisions,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:03:17.240 --> 00:03:24.440
and navigate complex environments. Chatbots, like&nbsp;
ChatGPT, can generate human-like text for tasks&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:03:24.440 --> 00:03:30.360
ranging from customer support to creative writing.&nbsp;
That logo on the right is the chatbot that appears&nbsp;&nbsp;

