00:38:56.440 --> 00:39:01.640
there’s no doubt that AI’s role in networking&nbsp;
will only grow in the future. AI definitely&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:39:01.640 --> 00:39:05.640
has the potential to revolutionize network&nbsp;
automation, so I’m looking forward to what&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:39:05.640 --> 00:39:11.040
the future brings. I hope this video&nbsp;
